    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but like, the studies about crime rates seem pretty scientific compared to just talking about constitutional rights... surely the data is more of a \"fact\" than an \"argument\" about how the law should be read? wouldn't you say the statistical side is more objectively true?",
